---
title: Cal Smart Roasted Tofu with Veggie Bulgur and Lemon Aioli
description: This light, bright meal of seasoned tofu is simplicity at its finest. Finished with a dollop of lemon aioli and served on a bed of savoury roasted zucchini and peppers tossed with bulgur, this is a dish you'll want to prepare again.

